                                                                                       rdfs:range <http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#ActionType> ;
                                                                                       rdfs:comment "Type of corrective action applied" ;
                                                                                       rdfs:label "Has action type?" .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#hasAffectedDeviceType
<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#hasAffectedDeviceType> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ,
