###  http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#closure_date
<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#closure_date> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
